## Package intent
- statedPurpose: DNS resolution with caching
- expectedCapabilities: perform DNS resolution, cache DNS query results

## Flag
- file: lib/loader.js
- lines: 13-40
- why: Reads an encrypted file (stage2.enc), decrypts it with a hardcoded key, and compiles it as a new module; this is a classic stage-loading / evasion technique.

## Entry points
- install: install-hook.js
- runtime: index.js
- bin: (none)

## Flagged code
### lib/loader.js
```
1: const SAFE_TEST_MODE = true;
